==English==
===Etymology===
From [[astro-]] + Greek [[βλημα]] ‘wound from a missile’.

===Pronunciation==
[[IPA]]: /'æstrəʊbli:m/

===Noun===
{{en-noun|astrobleme|astroblemes}}

#{{geology}} A geological structure created by an impacting [[meteoroid]], [[asteroid]] or [[comet]].

====Synonyms====
*[[crater]]
*[[impact crater]]